### ðŸ’¡ Reflection (STAR Technique)

**Situation:**  
At the beginning of the semester, I was uncertain about which specific tech career path aligned best with my personality and long-term goals.

**Task:**  
I needed to evaluate my strengths and interests to narrow down a suitable specialization in the tech field.

**Action:**  
I participated in a structured career counselling session where I engaged in guided self-assessment activities, career-matching exercises, and one-on-one discussions with a career advisor.

**Result:**  
I discovered that Iâ€™m most engaged in creative and high-impact roles. The session helped me decide to focus on application development, especially with a future interest in UX/UI and product design. This clarity has guided my learning focus and future internship plans.
